# applications.  While most users can probably do without looking into this,
# you may find some useful functions here.

CREDIT _team
  The following people currently contribute to polymake:
  Benjamin Assarf, Ewgenij Gawrilow, Katrin Herr, Sven Herrmann,
  Silke Horn, Michael Joswig, Lars Kastner, Benjamin Lorenz, 
  Andreas Paffenholz, Julian Pfeifle, Thomas Rehn, Thilo Rörig,
  Benjamin Schröter.

HELP help.rules

INCLUDE
  basic_types
  misc_functions
  permutations
  formatting_filters
  visual.rules
  geomview.rules
  postscript.rules
  povray.rules
  sketch.rules
  threejs.rules
  tikz.rules
  svg.rules
  lattice.rules
  tropical_parser.rules
  polydb.rules
  x3d.rules

# for algorithms shipped with polymake, as opposed to those imported from external software packages
label default

# activate them right now, to give other rules the chance to superpose it
prefer default

